import React from 'react'
import { Image, Item } from 'semantic-ui-react'

export default function Projects() {
    return (
        <React.Fragment>
            <Item.Group>

                    <Item.Image size='tiny' src='/images/wireframe/image.png' />

                        <Item.Header as='a'>Header</Item.Header>

                            pro 1

                <Item>
                    <Item.Image size='tiny' src='/images/wireframe/image.png' />

                </Item>
            </Item.Group>
        </React.Fragment>
    )
}
